## Project Structure

```
Infinix-ClawAnalytics/
├── claw_analytics/          # Core library
│   ├── ingest.py            # CSV / DB / API ingestion + column standardisation
│   ├── features.py          # RFM + trend feature engineering
│   ├── model.py             # Conversion-risk model training & inference
│   ├── cluster.py           # KMeans customer segmentation
│   ├── artifacts.py         # Parquet / JSON artifact persistence
│   ├── synthetic_data.py    # Synthetic transaction data generator
│   └── cli.py               # Click CLI entrypoints
├── api/
│   └── main.py              # FastAPI scoring API
├── dashboard/
│   └── app.py               # Streamlit analytics dashboard
├── tests/                   # pytest test suite
│   ├── test_ingest.py
│   ├── test_features.py
│   ├── test_model.py
│   ├── test_cluster.py
│   ├── test_synthetic_data.py
│   └── test_api.py
├── pyproject.toml
├── requirements.txt
└── README.md
```

