## Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `CLAW_MODEL_PATH` | `artifacts/model.joblib` | Path to the trained model artifact |
| `CLAW_CLUSTER_PATH` | `artifacts/cluster_model.joblib` | Path to the cluster model artifact |
| `CLAW_SCORES_PATH` | `artifacts/scores.parquet` | Path to the scored customers file (dashboard) |

